{
  "texts": [
    "However, the effect of PCR on BI and PU in the context of metaverse adoption in education has not yet been explored, which will be a key contribution of this study.",
    "Hence, it is argued that.",
    "H7: \"Perceived cyber risks (PCR) significantly and negatively affect perceived usefulness (PU)\".",
    "H8: \"Perceived cyber risks (PCR) significantly and negatively affect behavioral intention (BI) to use the metaverse\".",
    "PEU refers to the extent to which an individual perceives that using a given technology is easy and effortless (Davis et al., 1989)."
  ]
}